對大陸廠都係唔可以放棄既市場，一定會照用Google。"},{"pid":"563c39694af6ac91278b45f1ea2521aede8ef050","tid":1238782,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bb03e4bb84de965cc4e612872884a365d89d6c2e","tid":1238782,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e24ed33e481a90e1b36650d96950894237a3107c","tid":1238782,"uid":55951,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b6ed4a6d4de8fd6623735d2717ab162ee3b61b2d","tid":1238782,"uid":24576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"爺爺落order, 支那廠通通都要執行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:27:15.000Z","msg":"咁你又太高估支共對呢啲企業嘅控制力<br />\n坦白講，你諗到嘅佢會唔知？問題係佢推唔郁呢班大企業做嘢啊嘛<br />\n一停android，美國一定地圖炮咁停所以有支那廠用高通，之後ARM又跟隊MTK又要跟，咁未即係等於叫佢哋自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屎為已經示範咗俾其他支那廠睇，要ban的話係wifi ,Bluetooth , sd card都無得你用，你支那係唔係夠膽咁玩先，你唔係覺得支那廠是不能取代嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:27:16.000Z","msg":"北韓 伊朗 俄羅斯死左未？中國要撐既話真係可以撐到底"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:09:06.000Z","msg":"北韓伊朗同死左有咩分别，科技發展同經濟發展停頓，前者靠維穩死撐，後者靠石油勉強支撑<br />\n<br />\n俄仔前幾年俾人沽盧布都低調左好多啦<br />\n<br />\n就憑你中國？"},{"pid":"ebf4525674b7e4c9de962475eff56a9ec447bdc4","tid":1238782,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d8777165335d64cbc357be22bb88b5b1138b0fd","tid":1238782,"uid":226155,"like":2,"dislike":46,"score":-44,"quote":{"pid":"d07531035914caa73d2ad0fd6b17222928bc24af","tid":1238782,"uid":261530,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:52:50.000Z","msg":"試下支那廠拉大隊轉OS，睇下邊個傷D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:10:12.000Z","msg":"到時有問題，咪又